description_for_human: useful when you want to generate a new real image from both the user description and depth image.
description_for_model: useful when you want to generate a new real image from both the user description and depth image. like: generate a real image of a object or something from this depth image, or generate a new real image of a object or something from the depth map. The input to this tool should be the image_path and the user description
